So happy to finally be announcing that I will be hosting my second makeup class with @blessingmariah , at the second Mascara & Moscato event on June 3, 2023!🥂💄

If you missed the first one, heres your second chance! Tickets are officially on sale & after pay is available. Each ticket includes admission to the event, lunch, cocktails and a makeup goodie bag. 

Mascara & Moscato is a place to meet new people who share the love of makeup & the passion to learn or sharpen their skills. This year, we’ll be focusing on all things SKIN✨ as well as addressing the difficulty of finding the right foundation shade especially as a WOC. We’ll also cover shade matching, skin prep how to create a smooth flawless beat and more! 

Tickets are limited so be sure to secure your spot soon!

Still not over this day, Everything was so perfect. I’ll never get used to people showing an interest in my artistry, it means so much. As makeup artist, we’re often our own worst critic but this day was everything I needed to wipe away any lingering self doubt. I can’t thank you beautiful ladies enough for the immense amount of love & support that was shown🤎 There was really so much love & sisterhood in this room to say some of us just met an hour ago lol. 

  Leading up to the event, I can’t say I was nervous but, day of?! Yea I might’ve been sweating a little 🙃😅. But not even 10 minutes after stepping into this room, all nervousness was gone. The vibes at #mxm23 were THAT great! It felt like a safe space. Truly an amazing experience ✨

  You do it everytime @blessingmariah , I know how serious you take your creative projects & I can’t thank you enough or even express how much it means when you trust me to be apart of them. You’re forever giving me my flowers & telling me how proud you are of me & I’m equally as proud of you! 

  Thank you to everyone that played a part in making this day possible. @neeahjay , you’re literally my SISTER! Thank you for showing up & supporting me. Thank you @_fatusworld for agreeing to be my model, Coming over my house between a busy work schedule for multiple trial runs and just being so patient, sweet & easy to work with! And thank you to my friends that wished me luck, shared encouraging words before the event and even followed up with me immediately after with such excitement to hear how things went. It meant alot to know you guys cared & to see that my joy is your joy as well🥹💗🫶🏽

Blessed. 

#Mxm23 #MakeupBychochoana
